629
00:54:09,160 --> 00:54:14,120
put it in a quantum superposition at two different locations.

630
00:54:14,120 --> 00:54:19,160
Then, subject one of them to a magnetic field, rotating it by 2 pi radians,

631
00:54:19,160 --> 00:54:25,080
inducing the minus sign. Finally, recombine the electrons.

632
00:54:25,080 --> 00:54:30,200
In the end, you'll find interference effects stemming from the minus sign.

