00:54:55,320 --> 00:54:59,800
you about. Real projective space. If you take the

640
00:54:59,800 --> 00:55:03,560
two sphere and identify antipodal points as the same

641
00:55:03,560 --> 00:55:06,840
point, you create a topological space known as

